title: Full Body Calorie-BURN Elliptical Interval Workout | Sunny Studios
description:
Burn significant calories with our full body elliptical interval workout. Achieve an intense, low impact, calorie burning, cardio workout. Follow along Sunny Trainer Matt on this Full Body Calorie-BURN Elliptical Interval Workout. With the ability to add resistance and involve your upper body while using the full range of motion handlebars, you can create a unique workout experience that can help you move towards your health and fitness goals. 

This workout is great for those who are new to interval training and need extra guidance on how to use them properly during elliptical based workouts. Follow along with Sunny trainer Matt as he guides your through the warmup, interval, and cooldown. 

Workout Details:

Warm Up:

 1 minute - Full Body (light resistance)
 1 minute – Upper Body Focus (moderate resistance)
 1 minute – Lower Body Focus (moderate resistance)
 1 minute – Full Body (moderate resistance)
 1 minute – Full Body (high resistance)

Intervals:

Round #1
 1 minute – Lower Body (high resistance)
 1 minute – Upper Body (high resistance)
 1 minute – Full Body (high resistance)
 (Recover 1 minute)

Round #2 (increase pace)
 1 minute – Lower Body (high resistance)
 1 minute – Upper Body (high resistance)
 1 minute – Full Body (high resistance)
 (Recover 1 minute)

Round #3 (increase/hold pace)
 1 minute – Lower Body (high resistance)
 1 minute – Upper Body (high resistance)
 1 minute – Full Body (high resistance)

Cool Down:
 2 minute – Clear resistance

END WORKOUT
